  <name>Elelem</name>
  <summary>A friendly assistant with LLM</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Elelem is a user-friendly LLM client supporting both Ollama and OpenAI APIs. Create
      personalized assistants with pre-configured prompts or interact without predefined prompts.
      Elelem enhances productivity with its intuitive interface and robust functionality.</p>
  </description>
